rt Von Hagge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_von_Hagge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_von_Hagge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It features undulating fairways, challenging water hazards and strategically placed bunkers.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The course demands precision off the tee and strategic prowess on approach shots.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It should be a fine stage for Olympic golf.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are 10 players our model likes this week:  (current odds from DraftKings)  1.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DraftKings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DraftKings\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DraftKings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DraftKings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xander Schauffele (+550):Fresh off his second major title of the season, Schauffele enters the Olympics as our favorite.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seemingly has no weaknesses.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The defending gold medalist.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scottie Scheffler (+330):From convict to Olympian\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tongue-in-cheek, but after a season that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s included a green jacket, an emphatic rise to No.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\